How to Get Cookies

For private/restricted videos (followers-only):

Login to your IG/FB/YT account in Chrome

Install Get cookies.txt Extension

Export cookies

Save them as:

cookies_instagram.txt
cookies_facebook.txt
cookies_youtube.txt



